headline: New Thrive(TM) Program Helps Businesses Keep Waste Out of Landfills
summary: To help customers meet their sustainability goals, Kimberly-Clark Professional can now collect qualifying used dispensers1 to help make cement for building materials. ROSWELL, GA / ACCESS Newswire / September 9, 2025 / Kimberly-Clark Professional™ ...
